Say '''Boljoon''' et kumalima ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Cebu]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 15,027 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 117 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumadwa ya distrito. Say zip code to et 6024.	
															
